descriptionNullable:
### Context

I have recently been interested in GANs and I felt like there was a lack of curated datasets for Nepal.

### Content

The dataset contains over 50 images of Nepali portraits.

### Acknowledgements

This dataset was taken from Portraits of Nepal instagram page and google images.

### Inspiration

I believe that this image dataset could be used in face recognition, classification and GAN (Generative Adversarial Networks) for generating deep fakes.
title: Nepali Portraits Dataset
subtitle: Faces of Nepal dataset
